  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of vegetable oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add 4 cloves of minced garlic and cook for another minute, until lightly browned.",
    "Add the 200g baby spinach leaves and cook until wilted.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the soy sauce, honey, rice vinegar, and lacquer glaze.",
    "Pour the glaze over the spinach mixture and stir to coat.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and fleur de sel.",
    "Transfer the spinach mixture to a banana leaf and wrap it securely.",
    "Place the wrapped spinach on a baking sheet and bake at 200°C for 15 minutes, until the lacquer glaze is caramelized.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions before serving."
  ],
